---
description: Enforce clean architecture boundaries
globs: ["src/**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---

- Separate concerns strictly:
  - UI components: render + interaction wiring only.
  - Calendar logic: pure functions in dedicated logic modules.
  - State: centralized event source of truth.
  - Persistence: adapter-based boundary.
- Do not duplicate time/layout logic across components.
- Prefer small modules with explicit responsibilities.
- Keep business rules out of styling files and JSX templates.
